<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.8">
<l>īci pōmi ṉīṅki rēṉmi ṉirumi yiḷaittiruḷḷam</l>
<l>kūci yiṭṭī reṉṟu pēcuṅ kuvaḷai yaṅkaṇṇiyarpāl</l>
<l>nāca māṉa pācam viṭṭu naṉṉeṟi nōkkaluṟil</l>
<l>vācam malku taṇṭu ḻāyāṉ vatari vaṇaṅkutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [we] begin looking for a moral life, removing the noose of ruin</l>
<l>[That was] for the sake of ladies with lily-like eyes who [now] say,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Eeew! Please go away!</l>
<l>Please don’t sit here! You are falling over, coughing.</l>
<l rend="indent">You made [our] hearts cringe,”</l>
<l>We will worship at Badarī the one who wears fragrance-filled, cool tulasī.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
